txt.en: 'Very good, [placeholder]. I will see to these gems and make sure that Prince Ingór gets his fair share.'
Some of the Zhélruka seek precious gems from Gundabad.
The scout gives you a missive from the Zhélruka, seeking precious gems from Gundabad.
Bring the gems to Zádokh Flint-eye at Zidir-nesad
Zidir-nesad, The Steepset is located in Máttugard.\n\nYou should bring the gems to Zádokh Flint-eye at Zidir-nesad, The Steepset.
